Madrid 🛫 ➡️ Tokyo 🛬

With less than one week until #Tokyo2020, go behind the scenes with our presenter @ash_tulloch on her journey to the Olympic Games.  
 
#StrongerTogether #Olympics

node.text:
There is a light passed on from generation to generation, illuminating the very best of us.
No matter our differences, the #Olympics reminds us of how we are all #StrongerTogether.

Another step closer to #Tokyo2020 with Youth Olympic fencer turned popstar, @jacksonwang852g7.

node.text:
Sport climbing will make its Olympic debut at @Tokyo2020. 

How will this exciting sport change the Games and vice versa?

We asked some of its stars to weigh in.

@ifsclimbing
